spells.description:
Use: Command the Medichopper to attach to your target, absorbing 186,748 damage and granting them 1,316 versatility for 15 sec.

While attached, your healing spells have a chance to refuel the chopper, granting these bonuses to their host again. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Your spells have a chance to destabilize the void energy, releasing a corrupted fragment. Retrieving a fragment briefly infuses you with its power, increasing your Intellect by 11,559 for 15 sec.

Equip: When an ally falls below 20% health you shield them in darkness absorbing the next 163,759 damage taken.

This effect can trigger once every 30 sec and does not target devout allies.
